{"type":"message","id":"cf437153","parentId":"63459242","timestamp":"2026-03-24T20:17:31.487Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_t1a512gx1lwz_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5015\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=994\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] research/CONDITIONAL-CONTENT-ANALYSIS.md\r\n[mutation proposed] research/CONDITIONAL-CONTENT-ANALYSIS.md\r\n[master eafe7c8] pulse: 2026-03-24 161707\n 6 files changed, 284 insertions(+), 109 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 161707.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 161707.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 161543.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 161707 - The conditional content analysis is the critical next experiment to distinguish CFI (pattern information) from true causal influence. I need to implement this empirically to resolve whether high-CFI tokens like \"compression\" and \"causal\" are genuine causal drivers or just scaffolding.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"dawn-dune","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5015\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=994\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] research/CONDITIONAL-CONTENT-ANALYSIS.md\r\n[mutation proposed] research/CONDITIONAL-CONTENT-ANALYSIS.md\r\n[master eafe7c8] pulse: 2026-03-24 161707\n 6 files changed, 284 insertions(+), 109 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 161707.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 161707.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 161543.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 161707 - The conditional content analysis is the critical next experiment to distinguish CFI (pattern information) from true causal influence. I need to implement this empirically to resolve whether high-CFI tokens like \"com